com.lorin.continual.model

Class RankDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lorin.continual.model.RankDefinition

  • public class RankDefinition
extends Object
    Holds the ranking definition Can be changed and reset to default values Ranking rules: lowest (failure) value , highest rank Highest the rank , lowest the rank number E.g: prize one is the highest on the podium and has the lowest number
    Author:
    lorin
